# Dedicated Attendance Tracking System — Implementation Plan

## Goal

Enterprise-grade, anti-proxy attendance tracking with warden-initiated sessions, dynamic rotating QR codes, device binding, and GPS geofence validation.

---

## Architecture: Anti-Proxy Dual-Layer Verification

```
WARDEN                              BACKEND                         STUDENT
  │                                    │                               │
  ├─ "Start Roll-Call" ───────────────►├─ Create AttendanceSession     │
  │                                    │   (5-min TTL, rotating QR)    │
  │◄── Session QR (rotates 30s) ──────┤                               │
  │                                    │                               │
  │  [Displays on screen]              │    [Student opens app]        │
  │                                    │◄──── POST /attendance/mark ──┤
  │                                    │  { sessionToken, deviceFP,    │
  │                                    │    gpsLat, gpsLng }           │
  │                                    │                               │
  │                                    ├─ Validate:                    │
  │                                    │  1. Session active & token OK │
  │                                    │  2. Device fingerprint match  │
  │                                    │  3. GPS within hostel radius  │
  │                                    │  4. Not already marked        │
  │                                    │                               │
  │◄── Live: "43/50 present" ────────┤─── ✅ PRESENT ───────────────►│
```

### Anti-Proxy Layers

| Layer | Blocks | Bypass Difficulty |
|---|---|:---:|
| **Rotating QR (30s)** | Delayed screenshot sharing | Medium |
| **Device Binding** | Scanning from friend's phone | Very Hard |
| **GPS Geofence** | Scanning from outside campus | Very Hard |
| **One-time use** | Re-scanning same token | Impossible |

---

## Lost Device Re-Bind Flow

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Device re-binding requires **warden/admin approval** to prevent students from registering a friend's phone.

```
Student                    Warden/Admin                     Backend
  │                            │                               │
  ├─ Logs in on new phone ────►│                               │
  │                            │                               │
  │  "Device not registered"   │                               │
  │  [Request Re-bind] ───────►├─ Sees pending request ───────►│
  │                            │  Student: Deepika Gopal       │
  │                            │  Old: Samsung Galaxy A52      │
  │                            │  New: iPhone 14               │
  │                            │                               │
  │                            ├─ [Approve] ──────────────────►├─ Deactivate old device
  │                            │                               ├─ Bind new device
  │◄─────── "Device bound" ───┤◄──────────────────────────────┤─ Audit log entry
```

- **First login ever** → auto-binds (no approval needed)  
- **New device detected** → student sees "Request Device Change" → warden approves
- **Audit trail** → all device changes logged with timestamps and approver

