### Phase 2: Attendance Backend Module

#### [NEW] [attendance.module.ts](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/api/src/attendance/attendance.module.ts)

NestJS module: imports PrismaModule, exports AttendanceService.

#### [NEW] [attendance.service.ts](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/api/src/attendance/attendance.service.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `createSession(hostelId, createdById, gps, durationMin)` | Warden starts roll-call session with GPS anchor |
| `getSessionQR(sessionId)` | Returns current 30s TOTP token for the session |
| `markAttendance(sessionToken, studentId, deviceFP, gps)` | Validates all layers, marks PRESENT |
| `validateDevice(userId, fingerprint)` | Checks device is bound and active |
| `validateGPS(studentGps, sessionGps, radiusM)` | Haversine distance ≤ radius check |
| `upsertFromGateEntry(studentId, type, timestamp)` | Auto-update attendance from gate IN/OUT |
| `markLeaveAttendance(studentId, fromDate, toDate, leaveId)` | Bulk ON_LEAVE for approved leave days |
| `getDailyAttendance(date, hostelId?)` | All records for a date |
| `getStudentAttendance(studentId, from, to)` | Calendar data with percentage |
| `getPresenceBoard(hostelId?)` | Real-time in/out/leave counts |
| `getHostelSummary(hostelId, date)` | Aggregate stats |

#### [NEW] [device.service.ts](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/api/src/attendance/device.service.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `registerDevice(userId, fingerprint, deviceName, platform)` | First-time auto-bind |
| `requestDeviceChange(userId, newFP, deviceName, reason)` | Student requests re-bind |
| `approveDeviceChange(requestId, reviewerId)` | Warden approves → deactivates old, binds new |
| `rejectDeviceChange(requestId, reviewerId)` | Warden rejects |
| `getActiveDevice(userId)` | Returns current bound device |
| `getPendingRequests(hostelId?)` | Warden views pending re-bind requests |

