### Phase 3: Gate Integration

#### [MODIFY] [gate.service.ts](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/api/src/gate/gate.service.ts)

In [createEntry()](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/api/src/gate/gate.controller.ts#49-53), after creating the gate entry, call:
- `attendanceService.upsertFromGateEntry(studentId, type, timestamp)`
- Update `BedAssignment.presenceStatus` → `IN_HOSTEL` on IN, `OUT_CAMPUS` on OUT
- Auto-link active approved leave on gate OUT

---

### Phase 4: Leave Integration

#### [MODIFY] [leave.service.ts](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/api/src/leave/leave.service.ts)

In [wardenApprove()](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/api/src/leave/leave.service.ts#173-192), after status → `WARDEN_APPROVED`:
- Call `attendanceService.markLeaveAttendance(studentId, fromDate, toDate, leaveId)`
- Update `BedAssignment.presenceStatus` → `ON_LEAVE`
- Auto-create `GatePass` for the leave date range

