### Phase 5: Attendance Dashboard (Frontend)

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///d:/Apps/hostel/BMS_hostel/apps/web/src/app/dashboard/attendance/page.tsx)

**4 tabs:**

| Tab | Who Sees | Content |
|---|---|---|
| **Presence Board** | Admin, Warden | Real-time cards: In-Hostel / Out / On-Leave counts, student drill-down |
| **Daily Records** | Admin, Warden | Date picker → table with Name, USN, Room, Status badges, timestamps |
| **Roll-Call** | Warden | "Start Session" → shows QR + countdown timer + live student count |
| **My Attendance** | Student | Calendar with colored days, attendance %, gate history timeline |

**Roll-Call tab detail:**
- Warden clicks "Start Roll-Call" → enters duration (default 5 min) → GPS auto-captured
- Large QR code displayed (rotates every 30 seconds with countdown ring)
- Live list below: students' names appear as they mark present ✅
- Session auto-expires, remaining students marked ABSENT

**Student "My Attendance" tab:**
- Calendar month view: 🟢 Present, 🔴 Absent, 🔵 On Leave, 🟡 Late
- Attendance % bar with 75% threshold indicator
- "Scan Attendance" button → opens camera → scans warden's session QR

**Device Management (Student profile area):**
- Shows current bound device name
- "Request Device Change" button if on unregistered device

