## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. Create session → verify rotating QR changes every 30 seconds
2. Mark attendance with correct device + GPS → ✅ PRESENT
3. Mark attendance with wrong device → ❌ rejected
4. Mark attendance outside GPS radius → ❌ rejected
5. Mark attendance after session expires → ❌ rejected
6. Mark attendance twice → ❌ already marked
7. Device re-bind: request → approve → verify new device works
8. Gate IN/OUT → verify DailyAttendance auto-created
9. Leave approved → verify ON_LEAVE records for date range

### Manual Verification
1. Warden starts session → QR displays, countdown works
2. Student scans QR → attendance marked, count updates live
3. Lost device flow: student requests re-bind, warden approves
4. Student calendar shows correct daily statuses
5. Presence board shows real-time counts
